data.description: Hard to find a 3 Bedroom/2 Bath home on one level!!  Located in the popular community of Kingston Springs.  Only a couple of minutes to Kingston Springs Elementary School and walking distance to Harpeth Middle School, Harpeth High School and a 20 minute drive to downtown Nashville. This home has been updated with vinyl plank flooring, granite kitchen countertops, farmhouse sink, and a tankless water heater, new light fixures, plugs & switches, Metal Roof and Windows updated 5 years ago.  Primary Suite with walk in closet and ceramic tile shower.  From the carport you enter a large den with a gas fireplace and a 10x3 Walk in Closet.   A 16x20 Outbuilding with electricity is located outback and is perfect for a workshop or mancave and also has an attached screened in area 12x20.  Also a small metal building for extra storage.
